@@TJvStarfield
<TITLEIMG TJvStarfield>
JVCLInfo
  GROUP=JVCL.Graphics.Animations
  FLAG=Component
Summary
  A star field with moving stars.
Description
  Use TJvStarfield to show a star field with moving stars.

  * Use Stars to specify the amount of stars on the star field.
  * Use MaxSpeed to limit the amount of pixels a star will move per refresh event.
  * Set Delay to indicate the amount of time (in milli-seconds) between refresh events.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvStarfield.Active
Summary
  Indicates whether the stars are moving on the star field.
Description
  Set Active to True to move the stars on the star field. Set Active to False to interrupt the stars
  when they are are moving.

  Make sure to set MaxSpeed and Stars to a value greater than 0, otherwise the stars won't move.
See Also
  TJvStarfield.MaxSpeed, TJvStarfield.Stars

